\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/32?lang=spa&amp;id=p3#p3\">2 Nefi 32:3<\/a>.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-marker=\"9.\" id=\"note9\" data-full-marker=\"9.\">\n<p data-aid=\"163005434\" id=\"p_rQBpN\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/32?lang=spa&amp;id=p5#p5\">2 Nefi 32:5<\/a>.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-marker=\"10.\" id=\"note10\" data-full-marker=\"10.\">\n<p data-aid=\"163005482\" id=\"p_orZzB\">\u201cAprende sabiduría en tu juventud\u201d (<a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/37?lang=spa&amp;id=p35#p35\">Alma 37:35<\/a>).<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-marker=\"11.\" id=\"note11\" data-full-marker=\"11.\">\n<p data-aid=\"163005526\" id=\"p_a3BZI\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/1?lang=spa&amp;id=p1#p1\">1 Nefi 1:1<\/a>.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-marker=\"12.\" id=\"note12\" data-full-marker=\"12.\">\n<p data-aid=\"163005567\" id=\"p_sY0PU\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/34?lang=spa&amp;id=p18#p18\">Alma 34:18<\/a>; véase también el <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/34?lang=spa&amp;id=p17#p17\">versículo 17<\/a>.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-marker=\"13.\" id=\"note13\" data-full-marker=\"13.\">\n<p data-aid=\"163005610\" id=\"p_uqapb\">Biblia de Gedeón.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-marker=\"14.\" id=\"note14\" data-full-marker=\"14.\">\n<p data-aid=\"163005653\" id=\"p_z1rtv\">Véase <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/31?lang=spa&amp;id=p5#p5\">Alma 31:5<\/a>.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-marker=\"15.\" id=\"note15\" data-full-marker=\"15.\">\n<p data-aid=\"163005696\" id=\"p_xVrx4\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/nt/matt/5?lang=spa&amp;id=p6#p6\">Mateo 5:6<\/a>.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-marker=\"16.\" id=\"note16\" data-full-marker=\"16.\">\n<p data-aid=\"163005739\" id=\"p_hQ49y\">Véase \u201c<a href=\"https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/comeuntochrist/believe/god/how-to-pray\">Cómo orar<\/a>\u201d, LaIglesiadeJesucristo.org.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-marker=\"17.\" id=\"note17\" data-full-marker=\"17.\">\n<p data-aid=\"163005782\" id=\"p_iBQFA\">Véase <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/18?lang=spa&amp;id=p19-p20#p19\">3 Nefi 18:19\u201320<\/a>.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-marker=\"18.\" id=\"note18\" data-full-marker=\"18.\">\n<p data-aid=\"163005824\" id=\"p_cenit\">Véase Camille N. Johnson, \u201c<a href=\"https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/inspiration/the-savior-speaks-to-us-personally-uniquely-and-in-ways-we-will-understand\">The Savior Speaks to Us Personally, Uniquely, and in Ways We Will Understand<\/a>\u201d, <cite>Inspiration<\/cite>, blog, 15 de junio de 2022, ChurchofJesusChrist.org.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-marker=\"19.\" id=\"note19\" data-full-marker=\"19.\">\n<p data-aid=\"163005867\" id=\"p_f5G1Y\">Véase <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/2?lang=spa&amp;id=p16#p16\">1 Nefi 2:16<\/a>. Obsérvese cómo se enterneció el corazón de Nefi después de clamar a Dios.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-marker=\"20.\" id=\"note20\" data-full-marker=\"20.\">\n<p data-aid=\"163005910\" id=\"p_pdcoo\">Véase <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/19?lang=spa&amp;id=p11-p12#p11\">1 Reyes 19:11\u201312<\/a>: sentí la voz apacible y delicada llegar a mi mente y mi corazón; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/2?lang=spa&amp;id=p16#p16\">1 Nefi 2:16<\/a>: cómo Dios enterneció el corazón de Nefi cuando oró; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/enos/1?lang=spa&amp;id=p3#p3\">Enós 1:3<\/a>: el gozo de los santos (el Evangelio) penetró mi corazón profundamente; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/moro/10?lang=spa&amp;id=p4#p4\">Moroni 10:4<\/a>: orar con verdadera intención.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-marker=\"21.\" id=\"note21\" data-full-marker=\"21.\">\n<p data-aid=\"163005952\" id=\"p_qsIA4\">Russell M. Nelson, \u201c<a class=\"cross-ref\" href=\"/study/broadcasts/worldwide-devotional-for-young-adults/2022/05/12nelson?lang=spa\">Decisiones para la eternidad<\/a>\u201d, devocional mundial para jóvenes adultos, 15 de mayo de 2022, Biblioteca del Evangelio.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-marker=\"22.\" id=\"note22\" data-full-marker=\"22.\">\n<p data-aid=\"163005992\" id=\"p_wNxls\">Véanse <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/31?lang=spa&amp;id=p13-p14#p13\">2 Nefi 31:13\u201314<\/a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/18?lang=spa&amp;id=p10%2C13#p10\">Mosíah 18:8\u201310, 13<\/a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/20?lang=spa&amp;id=p37#p37\">Doctrina y Convenios 20:37<\/a>.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-marker=\"23.\" id=\"note23\" data-full-marker=\"23.\">\n<p data-aid=\"163006035\" id=\"p_nUIxd\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/32?lang=spa&amp;id=p3#p3\">2 Nefi 32:3<\/a>; véase también el <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/32?lang=spa&amp;id=p5#p5\">versículo 5<\/a>.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<\/footer>",
